assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Eltes Co.,Ltd. engages in AI security, digital risk, and DX promotion businesses in Japan. It offers social and internal risk management, on-line reputation management, digital credit, and security services. The company provides AIK order, a platform that connects individual and corporate customers who want to request security over the internet and security companies; and AIK sense, a security service for corporations, as well as DX conversion and promotion services. In addition, it supports information banks, smart-cities, and e-Government with construction of infrastructures for secure information exchange and heavy transactions based on distributed databases and personal authentication systems. Further, the company provides multiple solutions, including consulting for pre-avoidance of social risks to post-crisis response methods, as well as internal threat detection services. The company was founded in 2004 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan.
